OL,3,CPolice hunt vandals who covered
OL,4,Cancient Roman walls in graffiti
OL,6,FAncient walls thought to be more 2,000
OL,7,Fyears old have been vandalised in a
OL,8,Fcase of "heritage crime".
OL,10,FMembers of Cheshire Police's Rural
OL,11,FCrime Team received reports that four
OL,12,Fwomen were seen spray painting on a
OL,13,Fsection of Chester's historic city
OL,14,Fwalls just before 5pm on Monday 9
OL,15,FMarch 2026.
OL,17,FThe graffiti, which was found between
OL,18,Fthe city's Northgate and Cathedral,
OL,19,Fincluded the tags "Paris", "Lily", and
OL,20,F"Jasmine".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
