OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773252371
OL,3,CPolice hunt vandals who covered
OL,4,Cancient Roman walls in graffiti
OL,6,FChester's city walls were built
OL,7,Fbetween 70 and 80 AD, and are listed
OL,8,Fas a Scheduled Monument and World
OL,9,FHeritage Site.
OL,11,FThe walls are a major tourist
OL,12,Fattraction for the city, and most of
OL,13,Fthe structure is still in use today.
OL,15,FSpray paint has the potential to cause
OL,16,Fdamage to the stone used to build the
OL,17,Fwalls, and can be very expensive to
OL,18,Fremove.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
