CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773252371
OL,3,CPolice hunt vandals who covered
OL,4,Cancient Roman walls in graffiti
OL,6,FPC Jono Lightfoot said the walls had
OL,7,F"very strict" protections in law due
OL,8,Fto its status.
OL,10,FHe said: "This type of incident is a
OL,11,Fheritage crime and will not be
OL,12,Ftolerated. We would really like to
OL,13,Fhear from you if you were in the area
OL,14,Fand saw anything."
